{"tid":1338042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 狗準備清場","createTime":"2019-07-21T12:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T12:07:35.000Z","uid":175440,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70180fa9c95e4495ea79c8a1c2a77ce0698cdd4e","tid":1338042,"uid":175440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:04:32.000Z","msg":"【清場行動】<br />\n<br />\n今日遊行抵達灣仔終點後，部分人士前往西環一帶堵路，並破壞附近的汽車及塗污建築物的外牆。鑑於現場情況持續惡化，警方即將在西環向東面作出清場行動。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲，市民及駕駛人士應盡量避免行經相關地區。參與遊行完畢的人士在抵達終點之後，亦應盡快乘坐交通工具離開。在當區居住的市民及商戶，亦要注意留意自身安全，時刻留意警方的消息公佈及最新的狀況。<br />\n<br />\nBE WATER EVERYONE"},{"pid":"913b58291984ce0b4abb7fcf350450268f4bab5c","tid":1338042,"uid":280521,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:04:55.000Z","msg":"快走！"},{"pid":"553211b690c615ec83ab24d57d930fb747183451","tid":1338042,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:05:22.000Z","msg":"並破壞附近的汽車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩"},{"pid":"8fef7f54eea54d33552eb287c4c108cb0928aea4","tid":1338042,"uid":179824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"913b58291984ce0b4abb7fcf350450268f4bab5c","tid":1338042,"uid":280521,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:04:55.000Z","msg":"快走！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:05:30.000Z","msg":"p牌收陣聲先"},{"pid":"4b884c5c0e03d10404dd708fa62955f47051ba51","tid":1338042,"uid":33833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W6k9PRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW6k9PRh.jpg&h=5cbd0e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0GXYKD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0GXYKD.jpg&h=ea7265d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pHWdw4O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpHWdw4O.jpg&h=6744cc1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span sty